People ex rel. Maguire v. Purroy et al. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 31, 1892.) Action by the people on the relation of George J. Maguire against Henry D. Purroy and others.

*937Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and O’Brien and Ingraham, JJ.

No opinion. Motion denied upon payment by relator of $10 costs, and stipulating to argue at next term.
